<h2 id="bible_studies">Bible Studies for Adults</h2>
<p>
    <span class="bold">Monday Study:</span> at New Life are held at 12:00 PM at the church.
</p>
<p>
    <span class="bold">Friday Night Study:</span> is held at 6:30 PM at the church.
</p>
<p>
    All Bible studies begin with a meal together.
</p>
<p>
    During the Friday night studies, a Kids Club is offered for parents who attend the Bible study.
</p>
<p>
    The bible study topics are varied and are planned so they are appropriate for current events and the life stories of
    those who attend.
</p>
<p>
    Though the Monday studies are primarily attended by the seniors at New Life and the 6:30 PM study is attended by
    adults of all ages, all are welcome to come study and fellowship at either.
</p>

