<h2 id="youth">Youth</h2>

<p>
    At NLCF, the "Covenant" Youth meets together as regular as possible under the leadership of Rev. Karen Yee and
    Randy
    Fong. Various activities, studies and fellowship are planned. Throughout the year, the youth hold fund-raisers,
    take
    field trips and make mission trips.
</p>
<p>
    The "JeLo" Youth meet at various times with special field trips and fellowship meetings.
</p>
<p>
    Some of the exciting trips in the past include, skiing, camping, attending the annual national Baptist youth
    conference, and mission trips to Mexico, Puerto Ricao, and Washington D.C.
</p>
<p>
    In 2012, the College and Covenant Groups attended the American Baptist Youth Conference "Immerse" in Washington
    D.C.
    which included several missional opportunities.
</p>

